# Multinomial Logistic Regression

---
name: colors

## MLR

We used the 4th level as the baseline for Job Involvement.

First, we did a model with all of our variables: 
- Job Satisfaction
- Department
- Hourly Rate
- Years since last promotion
- Work life balance
- Age
- Number of Comapnies Worked
- Business Travel
- Environment Satisfaction
- Marial Status

The only variables statistically significant were Job Satisfaction, Business Travel, Environment Satisfaction, and Marital Status.

